Package: latva
Title: Exploratory R bindings for the latva C++ SEM library
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Encoding: UTF-8
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppEigen
Imports: Rcpp
SystemRequirements: C++23, cmake (to (re)build liblatva.a)
Description: Thin Rcpp wrappers exposing latva's C++ functions for
    interactive use. Not CRAN-bound; consumes the prebuilt liblatva.a.
